<DOCNO> LA102094-0012 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 090190 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 20, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
