<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWS BITES: LUKINS COMES HOME 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By KATHIE JENKINS 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In two years, Silver Palate co-founder Sheila Lukins will follow up her recent 
"All Around the World Cookbook" with "All Around the U.S.A. Cookbook."  
</P>
<P>
 "I thought of it while I was flying over the Cooper River, between Portland 
and San Francisco," she says. "I've already been to the Lima Bean Festival at 
Cape Maine, N.J." Today the world, tomorrow the New World. . . . KATHIE JENKINS 
</P>
</TEXT>
