the country: This must rank with one of the dumbest and most immoral deals this 
country has every made. To buy off a man whom President Clinton and other U.S. 
officials have described as "thug," "stooge" and "killer" is an unconscionable 
act. 
</P>
<P>
 One would imagine Cedras uses only one word to describe President Clinton and 
that is stooge . As defined by the dictionary, "one who serves as the butt of 
jokes." 
