 * Former Dodger pitcher Fernando Valenzuela, former USC basketball star Cheryl 
Miller and two San Pedro sports standouts -- Alan Sawyer, who played on John 
Wooden's first basketball teams at UCLA, and Joe Lovitto Jr., a former major 
league baseball player -- will be inducted into the San Pedro Sportswalk during 
ceremonies starting at 10 a.m. Monday in front of the Sheraton L.A. Harbor 
Hotel. 
</P>
