 Take a Hike for Child Safety 
</P>
<P>
 The Kiwanis Club of Newport Beach-Costa Mesa and the Irvine YMCA will host 
their 10th annual 5K walk/run on Sunday. Proceeds from the event will benefit 
child safety causes. 
</P>
<P>
