 * 
</P>
<P>
 IRVINE 
</P>
<P>
 Monster Mash for Tiny Haunts 
</P>
<P>
 Children age 4 to 10 are invited to take part in a city-organized Halloween 
Monster Mash Party the night before Halloween, Oct. 30, from 5 to 6:30 p.m. The 
party will take place at University Community Park, 1 Beech Tree Lane. 
</P>
<P>
 The party will feature games and contests. The cost is $12 per person. For 
more information, call the city's Community Services Department at 724-6610. 
