Column; Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA102094-0203 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 090381 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 20, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
