<HEADLINE>
<P>
BROTHER ACT AT CANYON 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Tom Messina, boys' and girls' track-and-field coach at Moreno Valley Rancho 
Verde High last year, has replaced his brother Bob in that position at Canyon 
High. 
</P>
<P>
 Bob Messina, whose boys were second in the Foothill League the past two 
seasons, now is Canyon's associated student body advisor. 
</P>
