</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 QVC Creates Single Offering: Faced with mounting costs and limited channel 
space on local cable systems, QVC Inc. is consolidating its Q2 home shopping 
channel with its onQ weekday service into a single seven-day operation.Q2 
President Candace Carpenter was let go along with about 20 other employees. The 
consolidation could eventually result in the layoffs of more than 100 workers, 
sources said. The consolidated operation will now be overseen by Mark Bozek, 
senior vice president of programming and broadcasting, and Caryn Lerner, senior 
vice president of merchandising and planning. 
</P>
