<TEXT>
<P>
 Richey Electronics Inc.: The Garden Grove electronic components distributor 
reported a 64% increase in profit for the third quarter, to $471,000, or 8 
cents a share, from $288,000, or 5 cents a share, for the 1993 third 
quarter.Sales rose 21%, to $22.8 million from $18.9 million. For the first nine 
months of 1994, profit tripled, to $1.4 million, or 23 cents a share, from 
$465,000, or 10 cents a share, for the corresponding period of 1993. Sales 
increased 42%, to $66.2 million from $46.7 million. 
</P>
