<P>
 Taco Bell: The Irvine fast food chain owned by PepsiCo Inc. reported an 
operating profit of $86.8 million for the third quarter ended Sept. 3, up 
nearly 13% from the $77.1 million posted a year ago.Sales increased 13%, to 
$829.8 million from $731.3 million. For the first three quarters of the year, 
operating profit rose to $175.1 million from $165.6 million. Sales were up 21%, 
to $2.3 billion from $1.9 billion. 
</P>
